{"type": "article", "id": 27431, "title": "在这家极简风格的理发店，平静优雅地换个发型", "description": "从发型到理发店，对简洁的欣赏都需要审美。", "date": "2016-05-27T14:00:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 15689, "name": "理发店"}, {"id": 28244, "name": "AS Barbershop"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 203, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163147sVXWT6rp7GL0g2CY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>如果你曾留心我们推荐过的理发店，会发现简洁的理发店更多。最极致的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/14618.html\">玛利亚理发店</a>只摆上了一张桌子，周围的环境都保持了洁净的白色，“剔除了一切冗余元素，将所有设计聚焦于理发这件事本身”。</p>\n<p>这家在巴西圣保罗的理发店<a href=\"http://www.felipehess.com.br/site/portfolio/barbearia-a-s/\"> AS Barbershop </a>也是一种极简风格，从完全刷白的墙面就可看出。临街的墙面被尽可能打开安装上玻璃门窗，使得路过的人可以看到理发店的全局并一眼感受到里面的风格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216313862xUAo7upt8zQkrE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163139FA5ykT0zs9C6iqGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03199174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">理发店的格局呈狭长形，有很长的纵深，5 个理发的座位并排在这个狭长的空间里，尽头是洗头、休息的地方。</p>\n<p class=\"\">用在墙面的材料只有两种，白瓷砖和浅色木材。白色的方形瓷砖铺满一面墙和天花板，隐约可见横竖交叉的线条，给人整洁干净的感受。地面的瓷砖颜色偏深面积更大，而另一面墙则使用更加明亮温暖的木材，可以看到竖线纹路，三种不同的颜色既有细微的区别又处在一个统一的极简环境中。<br></p>\n<p>在白色的环境中，室内的家具也有一种清晰的几何感，除了临街的梯形的门窗外还有椭圆形的镜子以及带有线条感的圆凳。室内的座椅、沙发使用了黑色或深棕色，没有任何彩色的装饰。黑色的线条强调边框，在纯净环境的对比下显得格外分明。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163140iOpsX3AhSKdyvBx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163140KhX9DMmctIE7V4r1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.18796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163141yr9qp51v0XzO4gja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163142B8RUQ31vjO2dorDn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">椭圆形镜子</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163142UaWftg1O4hSF8QKP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">三脚架的圆凳</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163143Wn82zoDcBXUGIlqb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">白色大理石储物柜</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163143sDOLeKCivHANuo9R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48514851\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163144BzLGEmqpQtnOs8C7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163144j3ZbsvTo4whk65GP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49750416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021631452CprWwyZoG3UkN1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49750416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163145jvElrW0YkL938RaT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49750416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163146B4nVflRpbvxLoD3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163147cedOWvxIQnHkSA8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49750416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/lifestyle/brazilian-barbershop-designed-by-felipe-hess-is-a-shrine-to-minimalism#158963\">wallpaper</a>、<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/787701/as-barbershop-felipe-hess\">archdaily</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"></div>\n\n"}